Exxaro Resources Ltd. (EXX)  may face a
strike next week after the South African coal miner decided to
go ahead with a plan to fire 300 workers, a labor union said.  Workers will vote on June 7 on whether to proceed with the
strike, the  National Union of Mineworkers  said in an e-mailed
statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nasreen Seria at 
 nseria@bloomberg.net  